Package io.github.thebusybiscuit.slimefun4.api.geo

Interface GEOResource

All Superinterfaces:
net.kyori.adventure.key.Keyed, org.bukkit.Keyed
public interface GEOResource extends org.bukkit.Keyed
A GEOResource is a virtual resource that can be thought of as world-gen. However it cannot be found in a World. This resource only exists in memory and can be retrieved through a GEOMiner or similar devices. A GEOResource can be detected via the GEOScanner.
Author:
TheBusyBiscuit
